	   <tr><td colspan=2>to get hand to hand up, you must use your weapons.&nbsp;&nbsp;dual wield goes up whether you have a weapon or hands.  I personally went for hands all the way past 20.  The result?  I was dishing out more damage than the twinks with fancy weapons.  They couldn't believe it.  The reason ?  They neglected their hand to hand skills.  At higher lvls your ATK goes up and Dly down with your fists.   At 30 I went to Dalnir and got a fighting baton and essence of Dol.  Then I went to Cazic and in less than 2 hours had my 1HB past 100.  So take it from me ---use hands.  You can get up your 1HB and 2HB later when you can afford the high priced weapons.  <br><br>-Silentfist Icuffs<br>30 monk on Quellious<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
