	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am level 14 and my sneaking is maxed out for my level.&nbsp;&nbsp;Yes, I am a monk.  The best way to raise sneaking is, I have found, to constantly keep on clicking on it.  Once you click it, click it again.  It still goes up when your sitting on your down time, so any time you can, just click it, the key is repetition.  It is very usefull to get by mobs, because you effectively become invisable to any mob, as long as they don't see you, you could actually stand less than a foot behind them and as long as your sneaking, they won't know your there.  It's usefull to sneak up on a mob, stop right behind it, click on your special attack, because it usually does more damage, and just attack it.  (Kinda plageristic off of a rogue's tactics, but OH WELL, it works!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
