	   <tr><td colspan=2>Very important point here...sneak does NOT make you invisible.&nbsp;&nbsp;It makes you QUIET.  Try ducking, and hear how loud you are.  Then turn on sneak, and go into "whisper mode."  Critters will still see you if you let them, and some critters will know you are there even if you're behind them (smell?)  But even if they see you, the aggro radius will be reduced, so you may be able to sneak by a guard, or get close enough to grab a corpse if the mob has it's back to a wall.  Also, don't forget the "sneak discount" you get by sneaking up behind merchants...buy for less, sell for more.<br>&nbsp;<br>Alerithon Tigerspirit<br>29 rank monk, E'Ci<br>Avatara</td></tr>
