	   <tr><td colspan=2>The earliest solution is risky.&nbsp;&nbsp;Get invis and go to Guk for the EE Bag.  At 19, you can work on the Orc side of Highhold for your chance at a Shralok's Pouch.  You can group up and go after Nillipus in Rivervale and take your chances on completing the quest for the Jum Jum Roots he drops which might yield a nice bag.  <br><br>Personally, I got my Shralok's Pouch at 20.  Now that I am rich, I bought a secondhand Box of Abu Kar (10 slot, extra large items, 100% weight reducing box that weighs 2 pounds)  Got it cheap because some folks have to have the very best, the Bag of the Tinkers, which weighs only 1 pound.  Both should sell from the merchant for about 5,200pp depending on your faction in Sol.<br><br>Mangudi, Revered Assasin<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
