	   <tr><td colspan=2>In my experience Tailoring is a beneficial skill for a Monk because you can tailor Cured Silk which is the lightest armor available to a lower lvl Monk in wt., and has a good AC too.&nbsp;&nbsp;Of course saying that, the next best skill to train in is Brewing, because you need to brew some Heady Kiola into the recipe to make Cured Silk.  Higher lvl Monks may have a better take though, I'm only in my teens.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
