	   <tr><td colspan=2>yes monks can solo. I have a 40th lvl monk on the tribunal server, and i found i could solo after lvl 30 if i found the right zone,with the right mobs. I spent a bit of time in lake of ill omen killing Sarnaks after i dinged 30, got me to about 32. I went to Frontier mountains after that and grouped till about 35-36. I could solo in FM after those lvls, fairly quickly too.But if i wanted faster exp i went to the overthere. Now at lvl 40 i a, starting to fight in the Dreadlands, but i will come back to FM to solo, cause i still get good exp there, but i may also solo spiders in FV cause i need silk for sewing. Anyway that has been my 2 cents, and monks rock , specially after 30 th lvl!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
