	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just a short note to recommend High Hold to you at your level (17-20).&nbsp;&nbsp;I grouped on the Gnoll side and repeatedly ran off the cliff up where we camped for the named gnoll.  I would literally hit the ground running, check for pops below, turn and run back up the ramp to see how the group was doing between battles.  I went up to level 20 and got my Safe Fall over the 101 Mastered level this way.  Also another way to raise Instill Doubt is to target the boat on long trips, or your group mates during lulls in battle.<br><br><br>Laredo, 39 Veeshan Monk<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
