	   <tr><td colspan=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;Another really good place to practice Safe fall, is in the Timorous Deep.  If you take the boat from Oasis, there will be a huge mountain off to the right of the docking place.  I was still takeing damage there at lvl 30.   I'm an iksar so it's the only "safe" route (other than a tele of course) to and from Kunark.  I've increased my skill three to four times in one run down the mountain, and it's a good way to kill time while waiting for the boat.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
