	   <tr><td colspan=2>A good place for safefall that I have used in the mid 20's is the hill to the left after crossing the stone bridge into South Ro.&nbsp;&nbsp;Was able to max out safefall within a couple of minutes at most levels.  Side note, a method that seems to work pretty well to raise disarm is in Befallen, give a rusty weapon to a wimpy skeleton and just hit the disarm hot key, when you disarm him hit the feign death and get right back up, he will stop attacking you, pick up the rusty weapon and give it back to him.  (Wash, rinse, repeat)  went up pretty quickly for me.  Better to practice in a relatively safe environment then when you will have more important matters on your mind, like is feign death going to work this time ;).<br>Good Journey,<br>Aaleb<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
